| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5106 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8067778a-b96c-53fb-ab3f-94063a1f8a4b"
